rows.label: tlk47100072_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh my. You weave a very curious tale
indeed, don't you?

rows.label: tlk47100072_01_msg0002
rows.name:
It's my instinct. Everyone carries their
destiny on their shoulders. And you
have the strangest one I've seen.

rows.label: tlk47100072_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Hey, can you tell me all about it when
your adventure's over? I'd love to hear!

rows.label: tlk47100072_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Phonexes love listening to stories.
Especially ones about heroes and
adventures!
